                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370703-1726-offence-1 t18370703-cd-83"></join>26th of June</rs>, 2 sovereigns, 4 half-crowns, and 9 shillings, the monies of <persName id="t18370703-name-602" type="victimName">
